    "For",
    "He grew up like atenderplant before Him,And",
    "like aroot outof dryground. No",
    "attractingform thatwe shouldlook upon Him,Nor",
    "appearancethat weshould desireHim. Like",
    "one",
    "fromwhom menhide theirfaces,He was",
