    "Godand afflicted. Andby",
    "Hisstripes wehave beenhealed.We all",
    "like",
    "sheep havegone astray;Each onehas",
    "turned tohis ownway,But Hewill",
    "see thefruit ofresurrection,And Hewill",
    "besatisfied."
